data.description: THREE BEDROOM, THREE FULL BATHROOM UPDATED PROPERTY IN PENNCREST SCHOOL DISTRICT. COUNTRY-STYLE SETTING IN COMFORTABLE SUBDIVISION. OPEN FLOOR PLAN. FRONT DECK WITH VIEW OF POND. KITCHEN OFFERS CONCRETE COUNTER TOPS, STAINLESS APPLIANCES, DINING AREA AND WALKOUT TO OUTDOOR KITCHEN AREA. FAMILY ROOM HAS A STONE SURROUND FOR WOOD BURNING STOVE. LOUNGE AREA WITH SPACIOUS BAR AND BATH. SECOND FLOOR WITH THREE BEDROOMS, HARDWOOD FLOORS AND TWO FULL BATHROOMS. OUTDOOR LIVING AREA HAS FIREPLACE AND KITCHEN AREA.
